<h2>Calagator</h2>

<p style="color: gray; font-size: 80%; margin-top: -2em">
Calendar Aggregation With Teeth</p>

<p>Calagator is an all-volunteer, open-source project to develop a collaboratively-managed calendar aggregation system for technical communities, such as user groups in the Portland, Oregon metro area. You will find the latest news on our <%= link_to 'blog', blog_path %> and <%= link_to 'discussion list', forum_path %>. We're always looking for new people to join us in making the best calendar aggregator possible.
</p>

<div id='coming_events'>
	<h2>What's happening?</h2>
	<h3>Today</h3>
	<%= render :partial => 'events/list', :locals => { :events => @events_today, :opts => {:dates => false} } %>
	<h3>Tomorrow</h3>
	<%= render :partial => 'events/list', :locals => { :events => @events_tomorrow, :opts => {:dates => false} } %>
	<h3>Later</h3>
	<%= render :partial => 'events/list', :locals => { :events => @events_later } %>
</div>
<div id='recently_added_events'>
	<h2>Recently Added</h2>
	<%= render :partial => 'events/list', :locals => { :events => @recently_added_events } %>
</div>
